    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition">
                <div type="textpart">
                    <ab>(S) In nomine domini dei eterni, anno ab incarnatione eius millesimo
                        centesimo octuagesimo septimo, quarto nonus augusti, indictione quinta.
                        Vendictionis contractus (…). Nos <persName ref="#people/3226"
                            >Castracanis</persName> olim filius <persName ref="#people/3214"
                            >Ubertelli</persName> et <persName><name ref="Castraleo"
                                >Castraleone</name></persName> filius eius et <persName><name
                                ref="Aigina">Aigina</name></persName> uxor eiusdem Castracanis et
                                <persName><name ref="Adalasia">Adalascia</name></persName> uxor
                        Castraleonis (…) vendimus et tradimus et huius rei gratia tradimus atque
                        concedimus tibi <persName><name ref="Petrus">Petroni</name></persName>
                        rectori <orgName key="#Hospitals" ref="#juridical_persons/3206"><rs
                                key="#Hospitals">hospitalis</rs>
                            <placeName key="#Hospitals" ref="#places/3207"
                            >Altepascensis</placeName></orgName>, recipienti vice et utilitate
                        eiusdem hospitalis (…) videlicet unam terre petiam positam in confinibus
                            <placeName ref="#places/3210" key="#Rivers #Roads">Putei</placeName> in
                        loco qui vocatur Vignale et commutationis nomine nobis pertinet a predicto
                        hospitale. Cuius confines sunt hii: caput unum tenet in <rs key="#Rivers"
                            >flumine Iussiana</rs>, aliu in terra <persName><name ref="Bernardus"
                                >Bernardi</name></persName> quondam <persName><name ref="Hugolinus"
                                >Ugolini</name></persName> et in <rs key="#Roads">via publica</rs>,
                        latus unum tenet in terra <persName ref="#people/3217">Adimarii</persName>
                        quondam <persName ref="#people/3218">Alberti</persName>, aliud in terra
                        dicti hospitalis et dicti Bernardi. Infra totam que est per mensuram ad
                        iustam mensurata perticam stariora quatuordecim. (…)
                            <foreign>Prezzo</foreign>: centum lib. quadraginta sol. minus bonorum
                        denariorum pisani conii nobis a te bene soluto. (…) <foreign>Pena</foreign>:
                        predicte terre et rei in duplum. (…) Actum <placeName ref="#places/3227"
                            >Gangalandi</placeName>. Signa manuus iamdictorum venditorum qui hoc
                        instrumenta fieri voluerunt, ut supra legitur. Signa manuum <persName
                            ref="#people/3234" key="#Witness">Buiamontis</persName> filii <persName
                            ref="#people/3227">Ugiccionis</persName> filii <persName
                            ref="#people/3228">Bonifatii</persName> et <persName key="#Witness"
                                ><name ref="Vitellio">Vitelli</name></persName> filii
                                <persName><name ref="Pacaloctus">Pacaloci</name></persName> atque
                            <persName key="#Witness"><name ref="Cuneradus">Cumradi</name></persName>
                        filii <persName><name ref="Adovarkus">Adovarki</name></persName> rogatorum
                            <rs key="#Witness">testium</rs>. (S) Ego <persName
                            key="#Writer #Notary #Judge"><name ref="Ieronimus"
                            >Ieronimus</name></persName>
                        <rs key="#Judge">iudex</rs> predictas mulieres interrogavi atque <rs
                            key="#Notary">notarius</rs> huic instrumento completione imposui.</ab>
                </div>
